ght\nspeak;Cres;I agree, but you might want to run, they're not thinking straight!|You'll be allowed sanctuary in Grahment, I'll try and smoothe this heat over for you.|The Sages I know would never organise this kind of hit job...\nspeak;Sal;Thank you!|Gang, run!\nmove_portrait;Sal;OffscreenRight\nmulti_remove_portrait;Sal;Oberon;Jevil;Cres\nspeak;Emeline;WAAAAH! CRUSH HER ALREADY!\nmulti_add_portrait;Skill;FarLeft;Esteban;FarRight\nspeak;Esteban;I will have them on a platter for you, your highness.\nspeak;Skill;GAH, ARCEIN SCUM! I will crush them as you wish, your brilliance!\nspeak;Emeline;*Sniff* Oh thank you Sir Skill!\nmulti_remove_portrait;Emeline;Skill;Esteban\nmove_unit;Sal;7,13\nremove_unit;Sal;;south\nflicker_cursor;11,7\nadd_portrait;Cornelius;MidRight\nspeak;Cornelius;Run all you wish, cockroach.|You cannot scurry away from divine punishment.\nend_skip\ntransition;close\nremove_portrait;Cornelius\nchange_tilemap;Ch3\nmusic;62 Prelude to Dispute\nmove_cursor;30,0\nremove_all_units\nadd_group;EnemyTeam;starting;immediate\nadd_weather;rain\ntransition;open\nadd_group;PlayerTeam;PlayerTeam;immediate\nspawn_group;PlayerTeam;south;PlayerTeam;normal\nadd_portrait;Sal;MidRight\nend\nif;game.check_alive('Nako')\nadd_portrait;Nako;FarRight\nend\nspeak;Sal;Gah! We need to make a break for it...|There!\nmove_cursor;0,12\nadd_region;Escape;0,11;1,3;event;Escape\nregion_condition;Escape;unit.nid =! \"Sal\"\nadd_region;EscapeSal;0,11;1,3;event;Escape\nregion_condition;EscapeSal;len(get_player_units()) == 1\nflicker_cursor;0,11\nflicker_cursor;0,12\nflicker_cursor;0,13\nspeak;Sal;That way should help us get back...|It may be guarded, but it's the way home alright.|Whoever that assassin was, clearly tipped someone off...\nmove_cursor;Sal\nif;game.check_alive('Aerial')\nadd_portrait;Aerial;Left\nspeak;Aerial;Seems weird, right?|But like, who would frame Sages?\nif;game.check_alive('Nako')\n    speak;Nako;I can hardly believe him to do such wrongs either...|But poor Elias... If only his wounds were not so servere we could have saved him...\nend\nif;game.check_alive('Smoke')\n    add_portrait;Smoke;OffscreenLeft\n    move_portrait;Smoke;FarLeft\n    speak;Smoke;I guess we need Sage advice right now to get out of this mess...|Eh? Eh?\n    speak;Sal;Not now.\n    speak;Smoke;Sorry. Let's make our move...|Though I smell enemies in hiding...|Best be careful, huh?\nend\nspeak;Sal;Onward everyone, quickly now!\nspeak;Sal;I will leave last, I won't leave anyone behind!;;;;;;convo-red\nadd_weather;switch_tile;0,11\nadd_weather;switch_tile;0,12\nadd_weather;switch_tile;0,13\n"
